1. *Zaglavio* se ključ u bravi. (The key got stuck in the lock.)
2. Nisam mogao da otvorim prozor, *zaglavio* se. (I couldn't open the window, it got stuck.)
3. Marko je *zaglavio* u saobraćajnoj gužvi. (Marko got stuck in traffic jam.)
4. U knjizi koju čitam, glavni junak se često *zaglavljuje* u teškim situacijama. (In the book I'm reading, the main character often gets stuck in difficult situations.)
5. Kada sam pokušao da promenim kanal, daljinski upravljač se *zaglavio*. (When I tried to change the channel, the remote control got stuck.)
6. *Zaglavila* se hrana u grlu, morala sam da popijem vodu. (The food got stuck in my throat, I had to drink water.)
7. Auto je *zaglavljen* u blatu, treba nam pomoć. (The car is stuck in the mud, we need help.)
8. Kada smo putovali kroz planinu, voz se je *zaglavio* u snegu. (When we were traveling through the mountains, the train got stuck in the snow.)